room_title: Escape room "The Artist" by Escape Point in Minot
review: Challenging but not unfair, by far one of the most creative and clever escape rooms I've seen! Certainly my favorite from Escape Point in Minot!

room_title: Escape room "The Artist" by Escape Point in Minot
review: We just finished "The Artist" and it was fantastic! The staff does a wonderful job and the entire experience was great! Can't wait to come back again!!
